{"tid":2099764,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲睇過政府專科門診皮膚科","createTime":"2020-07-08T13:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T16:26:56.000Z","uid":199985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"88394244c493c59b9891b351f830786ed5192ae9","tid":2099764,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜七日有5日塊面都敏感<br />\n會紅會痕會熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錢睇私家 但係政府有睇過敏免疫科（仲喺兒科）<br />\n本身有食物敏感（蝦）<br />\n最近發現食左甲殼類海鮮都會塊面敏感 而家介緊口<br />\n<br />\n想喺下次過敏免疫科覆診嘅時候<br />\n同醫生講下敏感得咁密嘅情況轉介<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我怕佢又比d好笠嘅藥膏例如elomet我搽就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時skin care已經用無香料無色素酒精嗰啲敏感皮膚適用嘅產品<br />\n但都仲係成日敏感 好影響我心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cfc58ef5377693159df7dde3257114b6b0dd01","tid":2099764,"uid":192732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"有排過 兩年後 之後冇去到"},{"pid":"80ef4cf15fd4b6f1700dcd99d450831f73d1fa28","tid":2099764,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6cfc58ef5377693159df7dde3257114b6b0dd01","tid":2099764,"uid":192732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"有排過 兩年後 之後冇去到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"巴打當時咩環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef7195e8d0a2c3cd7343af92480dc41fd7def10","tid":2099764,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2399da5a887e6b44f6918cd6e58a6a29bfbc8a","tid":2099764,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:18:41.00